title: S16 Ep105: Portals & The Haunted Forests of WWII Germany w/Anna Maria Manalo
itunes:title: Portals & The Haunted Forests of WWII Germany w/Anna Maria Manalo
description:
Darkness Radio presents Portals & The Haunted Forests of WWII Germany with Anna Maria Manalo

Dave & Tim are joined by guest Anna Maria Manalo as she returns to update us on the re-release and update to her first book. Portal: A Lifetime of Paranormal Experiences and fills us in on the new book that will be coming out this fall, The Way Through the Woods: A Child's Escape through The Haunted Forests of WWII Germany.  Fascinating looks at supernatural encounters from varying perspectives.


Get her first book here: https://amzn.to/3kYrtSn
